\n< Serena >Who will eat me... and fight over it...!
\n< Serena >Ugh! D-don't... lick me with your tongue...!
\n< Serena >Ah... If it continues like this...
\n< Serena >Eaten... I'm going to be eaten...!
\n< Serena >No... Are you enjoying... tormenting me...?

\n< Serena >You... I am... proud... of being a Gracia...
that's why... that's why...

\n< Serena >I won't beg for my life from you monsters! It's
useless to torment me! Who would cry for someone
like me!

\n< Serena >I-if you're going to do it... then do it all at
once...!?
\n< Serena >It... hurts... it hurts so much...!
\n< Serena >Inside me... something hot and sticky...

\n< Serena >I... Ahh... It's... gouging... Ogo!! It's being
shaved...!

\n< Serena >Haa, haa... What... What do you intend to do to me
any further?
\n< Serena >What is that... tool?... Huh, ah?

\n< Serena >W-What do you intend to do!? Stop it! Don't come
any closer, stop... gah!?
\n< Serena >S-Stop... Let go! Please let go! It hurts! Nooo!
\n< Serena >Haa, haa... Wha-what is this? Marks on my body...
\n< Serena >Huh!? Are you still planning to do it!? Nooo!
\n< Serena >Ngh!? Ahh! D-Don't move! That thick... it hurts!

'ああっ、た、叩くな！ゆれて…くぅぅ！'

'あそこが、ぐりぐり…抉れて…あぁっ。'
